snippet.title: Cannon Fodder
snippet.description:
"War has never been so much fun!  Go to your brother, kill him with your gun, leave him lying in his uniform dying in the sun."

This is a clip of the first two missions of Cannon Fodder.  If I didn't suck at the game, I wouldn't have lost Jops.

lyrics fixed (thanks brigand22!)
